@startuml Software-Engineering-DHBW_bikeminer

actor User

box "Mobile Apps" #LightBlue
    participant "Flutter App" as FlutterApp
    participant "Android App" as AndroidApp
end box

participant "FastAPI Backend" as Backend
database "MariaDB" as Database

== User Interaction ==
User -> FlutterApp : Open app
User -> AndroidApp : Open app (legacy)

== Authentication ==
FlutterApp -> Backend : POST /login
Backend -> Database : Verify credentials
Database --> Backend : User data
Backend --> FlutterApp : JWT token

== Location Tracking ==
FlutterApp -> FlutterApp : Start background location tracking
AndroidApp -> AndroidApp : Start GPS tracking (MapsActivity)

== Ride Data ==
FlutterApp -> Backend : POST /rides
AndroidApp -> Backend : POST /rides
Backend -> Database : Store ride data
Database --> Backend : Confirmation
Backend --> FlutterApp : Ride saved
Backend --> AndroidApp : Ride saved

== BikeCoin Update ==
Backend -> Database : Calculate BikeCoin reward
Database --> Backend : Updated balance
Backend --> FlutterApp : New BikeCoin balance
Backend --> AndroidApp : New BikeCoin balance

== Fetch User Data ==
FlutterApp -> Backend : GET /user
Backend -> Database : Fetch user data
Database --> Backend : User information
Backend --> FlutterApp : User profile and balance

== Ride History ==
FlutterApp -> Backend : GET /rides
Backend -> Database : Fetch ride history
Database --> Backend : Ride data
Backend --> FlutterApp : Ride history

@enduml